Topology:- ____________________________ | VersaDirector | |___________________________| | | | _____________|_______________ | WanCtrller1 | |____________________________| | | | | | | INTERNET/MPLS | | | |___ ______|__ ___|___ | | | | LAN1--+ CPE1 | | CPE2 +--LAN1 |________| |_______|
